WARNING: EARNEST POST! I cant possibly fit everyone into ten photos, but I just had a chance to make a flick with some of the most beautiful people I’ve ever had the chance to meet. My heart has grown immeasurably in such a short time as I fell in love over and over again with everyone involved. Finally, I know what the Grinch was going through. To be talented and capable is one thing, but for so many people to be unwaveringly kind is what will make this experience wholly unforgettable. Love you dearly, my compatriots. Until we meet again. ♥️
